These are Puzzles for 3x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-1::.
City: miami, colone, edinburgh, boston, nizza
5 different pets are kept: frog, mouse, horse, dog, goldfish
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, golf, soccer, volleyball
 1. the owner of the frog is the person traveling to boston##1
 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an even position##4
 3. the person traveling to colone is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the owner of the frog and the person traveling to nizza##2
 5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
 8. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
12. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |      5      |
| City         | colone    | edinburgh  | nizza | miami    | boston |
| Pet   | mouse     | horse   | dog | goldfish | frog   |
| Sport         | basketball | biathlon | soccer  | volleyball | golf        |

