.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, drawing, video-games, woodworking
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: soul, funk, jazz, electronic, country
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, lavender, coral, ivory, blood-red
 1. the person who likes coral is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of country is between the person who likes grey and the person who likes ivory##2
 3. the fan of country is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is in the middle##1
 7. the fan of soul is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 8. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
 9. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the fan of country is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
11. the fan of electronic is between the person who likes blood-red and the person who likes lavender##2
12. the person who likes ivory is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |        2        |     3      |         4          |     5     |
| Hobby   | video-games    | cooking         | collecting | woodworking        | drawing   |
| Music-Genre     | funk | jazz | electronic  | country | soul |
| Color   | coral       | blood-red      | ivory   | lavender           | grey      |

