.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-3::.
House: futuristic, ranch-style, townhouse, farmhouse, craftsman
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, golf, rugby, skateboarding, swimming
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, chaman, tiparillo, fonseca, vegafina
 1. the ranch-style house is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 2. the chaman-smoker is the person who's sport is golf##1
 3. the farmhouse house is in the middle##1
 4. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
 5. the futuristic house is between the chaman-smoker and the craftsman house##2
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
10. the townhouse house is the vegafina-smoker##1
11. the person who's sport is basketball is the tiparillo-smoker##1
12. the fonseca-smoker is between the person who's sport is golf and the vegafina-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |     5      |
| House    | townhouse | ranch-style    | farmhouse   | futuristic          | craftsman      |
| Sport       | rugby    | swimming | golf       | skateboarding | basketball |
| Cigar   | vegafina     | fonseca     | chaman | bolivar          | tiparillo     |

