.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-8::.
5 different games are played: chess, canasta, whist, snooker, backgammon
There 5 different types of food: cranberry, grapes, garlic, cauliflower, lime
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, metal, punk, r&b, techno
 1. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left##1
 2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 3. the person playing whist is between the person eating garlic and the person playing snooker##2
 4. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 5. the fan of r&b is the person playing chess##1
 6. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
 7. the fan of blues is the person playing snooker##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 9. the person playing canasta is on the far left or far right##3
10. the fan of punk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |       4       |      5       |
| Game         | chess | backgammon | snooker    | whist | canasta      |
| Food           | cauliflower | grapes | cranberry | lime    | garlic |
| Music-Genre   | r&b        | techno      | blues     | punk          | metal        |

